This doc describes the contribution rules to get a good development experience

## Project Mantra

readable rather than fast and short

"la optimización prematura es la madre de todos los males"

### Code

#### Documentation

Every function, route group, file, set of css or sass or generally every file/code created/edited by us will have a multiline comment with the autor, date created/updated and a description using the comment format of the language ej(php):

```php
/**
* @Autor Marco A. Gallegos
* @Date 2020/06/20
* @updated 2020/06/21 -> Marco A. Gallegos
* @Description this doc describes not obvious rules for the project "Coordinator Admin"
*
* @param [type] $var -> "description, if necessary"
* @return [type] $var -> "description, if necessary x2"
*/
```

#### Formating

Every line of code will have a identation like it was python code

#### Modules

every resource in laravel(controller, view) will be grouped into a folder called with the name of the module
